<Base
  title="AI Memory for Healthcare: Why Retrieval Precision Is Non-Negotiable | Tenure"
  description="Healthcare AI memory cannot rely on semantic search. Precision, scope isolation, and deterministic retrieval are safety requirements, not optimizations. Here's why."
>

